      "rationale": "Code verification relies on ANSYS Fluent's published method of manufactured solutions (MMS) test suite results and documented benchmark cases for incompressible rotating machinery flows. Additionally, in-house Taylor-Couette flow benchmark confirmed second-order spatial accuracy of the finite-volume discretisation.",
